Class FileRank

  • java.lang.Object
    • board.FileRank

  • public class FileRank
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a location on the chess board, with a file being the columns, and the rank notating the rows.
    Author:
    Sarah Squillace, Nikita Zala
